    </marquee>
    <p>Wade Ripple is transparent… and not only because he’s a Water element. He’s also emotionally transparent – an open book, observant, empathetic and bubbling with compassion. When he meets Ember – an element of distinctly different temperature – Wade can’t help but wonder about a future that may seem impossible on the surface. Can these two opposites form a bond that transcends their differences?</p>
    <h2>Wade Ripple</h2>
