<p>Bernie Lumen is a Fire element with a big, crackling personality that burns with pride… about his homeland, about his daughter, Ember, and about the shop he runs in Element City. He and his wife Cinder left Fire Land to provide a better life for their only child, bringing with them just their dreams. And make a better life is exactly what they did. Their neighborhood shop has become a destination for Fire elements, and Bernie is patiently awaiting the day Ember is ready to take it over. </p>
